These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rowing, weightlifting, skiing, sailing, handball
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, reggae, house, ambient, d&b
 1. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is the fan of reggae##1
 3. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is rowing##1
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the fan of d&b##5
 5. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of house##1
 6. the person who's sport is handball is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
 7. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
 8. the person who's sport is handball is not the fan of house##6
 9. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
10. the fan of classical is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
11. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
12. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the fan of classical##1
13. the fan of ambient is not to the left of the fan of house##8
14. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the person who's sport is handball and the fan of house##7
15. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5     |
| Sport        | weightlifting | skiing | handball | sailing     | rowing    |
| Music-Genre   | house | d&b       | classical   | ambient | reggae |

