.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-8-2::.
House: cape-cod, wooden, colonial, cottage, modern
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, blood-red, ivory, purple, emerald
 1. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
 2. the person who likes emerald is not to the left of the person who likes chestnut##8
 3. the wooden house is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
 4. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5
 5. the modern house is not to the right of the cape-cod house##8
 6. the person who likes blood-red is not the cape-cod house##6
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 9. the wooden house is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
10. the modern house is not to the right of the cape-cod house##8
11. the cape-cod house is the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| House   | cottage | modern    | cape-cod | wooden  | colonial |
| Color   | chestnut  | purple | emerald      | blood-red | ivory |

