There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, grey, green, apricot, azure
1. the pakistani is not to the right of the person who likes azure##8
2. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
3. the british is between the person who likes apricot and the egyptian##2
4. the british is the person who likes green##1
5. the italian is in the middle##1
6. the pakistani is on the left of the person who likes chestnut##1
7. the pakistani is not to the left of the italian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |       3        |     4     |     5     |
| Nationality           | egyptian | british | italian | pakistani | argentine  |
| Color   | grey  | green        | apricot          | azure     | chestnut |

