 5. the person who growsdahlia is in an even position##4
 6. the person watching scientific movies is not to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
 7. the person who growsdahlia is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
 8. the person watching horror movies is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
 9. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdahlia##5
10. the person watching romance movies is the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
