 7. the vegafina-smoker is the vegafina-smoker##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who likes grey##2
 9. the montecristo-smoker is not to the right of the vegafina-smoker##8
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
11. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
12. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who likes green##1

